<p>Sierra Virginia Community (SVC) is a 501-c nonprofit organization dedicated to advancing the success of community members and the Sierra Leonean culture and building and improving relationships through soccer and other social activities.<br>SVC comprises various professionals ranging from engineers, artists, health, IT, and other seasoned professionals, who comprise many of the Sierra Leone Community in Virginia, one of the oldest and most diverse Sierra Leonean communities in the United States.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>With a diverse and dynamic executive team, we have made transparency, accountability, and inclusivity the foundation for the growth and development of the community. We are constantly growing and welcome new members to this vibrant community. We are currently located in Alexandria, Virginia.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://svcus.org/contact/" data-type="page" data-id="73">Contact us for information about membership and other questions</a></p>
